stnut, 2015<ref name=\"Pedigree\">{{cite web|url=https://www.jbis.jp/horse/0001296350/pedigree/|title=Eskimo Kisses (USA)|publisher=JBIS |date=2017-11-28 |accessdate=2019-03-29}}</ref> \n|f = To Honor and Serve(USA) <br> 2008\n|m = Silver Colors(USA) <br> 2007\n|ff = [[Bernardini (horse) | Bernardini]] (USA) <br> 2003\n|fm = Pilfer (USA) <br> 2001\n|mf = Mr. Greeley (USA) <br> 1992\n|mm = [[Winning Colors (horse) | Winning Colors]] (USA) <br> 1985\n|fff = [[A.P. Indy]] (USA)\n|ffm = [[Cara Rafaela]] (USA)\n|fmf = [[Deputy Minister (horse) | Deputy Minister]](CAN)\n|fmm = Misty Hour(USA)\n|mff = [[Gone West]] (USA)\n|mfm = Long Legend (USA)\n|mmf = [[Caro (horse)|Caro]] (IRE)\n|mmm = All Rainbows (USA)\n|ffff = [[Seattle Slew]]\n|fffm = [[Weekend Surprise]]\n|ffmf = [[Quiet American (horse) | Quiet American]]\n|ffmm = Oil Fable\n|fmff = [[Vice Regent]]\n|fmfm = Mint Copy\n|fmmf = [[Miswaki]]\n|fmmm = Our Tina Marie\n|mfff = [[Mr. Prospector]]\n|mffm = Secrettame\n|mfmf = [[Reviewer (horse) | Reviewer]]\n|mfmm = Liang\n|mmff = Fortino\n|mmfm = Chambord\n|mmmf = Bold Hour\n|mmmm = Miss Carmie\n|}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n[[Category:2015 racehorse births]]\n[[Category:American racehorses]]\n[[Category:Racehorses bred in Kentucky]]\n[[Category:Racehorses trained in the United States]]\n[[Category:Thoroughbred family 23-b]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American thoroughbred racehorse}}\n{{Infobox racehorse\n| horsename = Eskimo Kisses\n| image_name = \n| caption = \n| sire = To Honor and Serve<ref name=\"BC\">{{cite web|url=http://www.breederscup.com/horse/eskimo-kisses|title=Eskimo Kisses|publisher=Breeders Cup |date=March 28, 2018 |accessdate=March 29, 2019}}</ref> \n| grandsire = Bernardini\n| dam = Silver Colors\n| damsire = Mr. Greeley\n| sex = [[Mare]]\n| foaled = February 26, 2015 <ref name=\"EQL\">{{cite web|url=https://www.equibase.com/profiles/Results.cfm?type=Horse&refno=9875220&registry=T&rbt=TB|title=Eskimo Kisses|publisher=Equineline |dat